This code helps you to get the entity files of the site which you will require while quering through Linq.
Place this entity file in your VS project and you can query the lists using Sharepoint Linq.
Before you try this you need to add Microsoft.SharePoint.dll into your project and add the reference of the same in your code.
Later on you can use the Linq to get the data from any list in the site as show above .
Linq is very fexible and very fast than any other methods compared to Spquery or the SharePoint object model .
It has few other advantages like complete sorting as well as filtering the data is also fast and easy in Linq.
